About Event

​Wake up with Turbine: fuel your JPM morning with cold brews, good conversations, and insight into how pharma is leveraging virtual cell technology today.

​We’re taking over Bluestone Lane to bring together biotech leaders, pharma R&D decision makers, and simulation-curious innovators for a morning of learning, networking, and hands-on exploration of our Virtual Lab.

​7:00-8:00 AM - Live Q&A with Szabi Nagy, Turbine Co-founder & CEO
